state.title: you
state.stateText: You have elected to declare war on:

state.title: they
state.stateText: This clan has declared war on you:

uiEntry.title: your_allies_tx
uiEntry.tooltip: You can call upon these nations to join you in this war, but they may turn you down.||You will see which nations have joined you once you have declared war.||It is possible for both sides to have allies in common.||If this is the case and war is declared, the allies will have no choice but to break one of the alliances.

uiEntry.title: their_allies_tx
uiEntry.tooltip: The nation you're about to declare war on may call upon their allies to bear arms against you.||If their allies are also allies of yours, or just very powerful, you may want to cancel your declaration of war.||However, keep in mind their allies may refuse the call to arms.||You will find out which allies have joined them once you have declared war.

uiEntry.title: button_ok_declare
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("diplomacy_panel"))
function OnSelect() parent:LuaCall("OkDeclareWar") end

uiEntry.title: button_cancel_declare
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("diplomacy_panel"))
function OnSelect() parent:LuaCall("ClearSubPopups", false) end

uiEntry.title: button_ok_declared
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("diplomacy_panel"))
function OnSelect() parent:LuaCall("OkDeclareWar", true) end

uiEntry.title: checkbox
uiEntry.tooltip: When this box is checked you will ask your allies to join you in war.||Note that this box is always automatically checked when you declare war.||Your allies may turn down your request, so make sure you're ready to fight alone if needs be.||If a nation is the aggressor then an ally can turn down the request without breaking the alliance.||If the request is made by a defending nation then the ally must help or break the alliance with them.

uiEntry.title: call_help_tx
uiEntry.tooltip: When this box is checked you will ask your allies to join you in war.||Note that this box is always automatically checked when you declare war.||Your allies may turn down your request, so make sure you're ready to fight alone if needs be.||If a nation is the aggressor then an ally can turn down the request without breaking the alliance.||If the request is made by a defending nation then the ally must help or break the alliance with them.

uiEntry.title: joined_tx
uiEntry.tooltip: These allies have joined the war!

uiEntry.title: refused_tx
uiEntry.tooltip: These allies have refused a call to war.

state.title: NewState
state.stateText: Some of your allies have refused to join your side:

uiEntry.title: button_ok
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("diplomacy_panel"))
function OnSelect() parent:LuaCall("OkWarDeclared") end
